  <brief_title>IBSR Meditation Technique for Teachers' Burnout</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Inquiry Based Stress Reduction (IBSR) Meditation Technique on Levels of Burnout and Wellbeing Among Teachers.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
