  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the effect of Inquiry based stress reduction
      (IBSR) meditation technique on levels of burnout and wellbeing among teachers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Teachers' burnout is a well-known phenomenon with personal and professional implications. The
      current study investigates the effect of inquiry based stress reduction (IBSR) technique on
      burnout and well-being among teachers.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
